Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.15,0:00:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something only she and I can tell you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A story of one of the secrets of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.11,0:01:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It looked like a pool of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.16,0:01:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She ran out of the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.76,0:02:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Praying with all her heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.97,0:02:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,she crossed the shrine gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.38,0:03:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I wonder if what I saw that day was just a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But it wasn't a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.81,0:03:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That summer day, up in the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,we fundamentally altered the nature of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.39,0:04:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna rain again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.14,0:04:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it'd finally cleared up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.81,0:04:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We ran into a typhoon on the island, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.07,0:04:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.11,0:04:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.14,0:04:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.14,0:05:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That was one hell of a storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.36,0:05:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure you don't want any, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I don't have much of an appetite.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.57,0:05:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Thanks for the treat then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mention it! You saved my life after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.95,0:05:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that was a close one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.50,0:06:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,it's the first time I saved someone's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, I wonder if they have beer here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I get you one?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So expensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.35,0:06:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A grown-up man scrounging on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokyo is scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.59,0:06:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's raining again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.63,0:06:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you come to Tokyo, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ehm... I'm visiting a relative.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:06:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Summer vacation starts early at my school, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, feel free to contact me if you ever need help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.98,0:07:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Shower's 280 yen for 20 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.38,0:07:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It started pouring again all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you ever learn? It's a pain to clean up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.95,0:07:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,For real!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, are you really a university student?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.79,0:07:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Your ID?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.37,0:07:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a job for kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokyo is scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to start saving.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, don't sit down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.24,0:08:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,All you can drink for 1800!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey master!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.51,0:08:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you a minor?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.84,0:08:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit messing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokyo is scary, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.34,0:09:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Never again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, who's this kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.27,0:09:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.31,0:09:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,On the floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you, are you a customer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... is he gonna be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.03,0:09:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:09:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.43,0:10:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be a toy gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm, This...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.49,0:11:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for you. Don't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that's your only dinner in like, three days?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.42,0:11:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,In all the sixteen years of my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.89,0:11:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that one
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,was the most delicious dinner I've ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:12:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, when can we meet again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.53,0:12:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How about the day after tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! I found a nice café.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll book us a table.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.28,0:12:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,See you, Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye, Ayane.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A grade schooler?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.67,0:12:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky me! I was hoping to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.92,0:12:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Kana.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.84,0:12:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.22,0:12:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you curl your hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.59,0:12:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You could tell? How does it look?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.89,0:12:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You look great! Super cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokyo is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.45,0:12:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this even work?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:13:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.13,0:13:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Morishima from the call earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Mr. Suga around?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.14,0:13:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Mr. Suga?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.27,0:13:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. {\alpha&HFF&}Suga?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.31,0:13:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Suga?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, this isn't appropriate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.90,0:13:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, the new assistant Kei told me about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? No, I haven't—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Natsumi. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, someone else to do the grunt work!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.84,0:13:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.09,0:13:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You looked at my boobs, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I did not!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your name, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.60,0:13:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Hodaka Morishima.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.77,0:13:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hodaka. That's a beautiful name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you work here, Natsumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.61,0:14:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wanna know about me and Kei?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.73,0:14:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.07,0:14:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Amusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.36,0:14:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's exactly like you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you lose some weight?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.96,0:14:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't tell me you went gambling again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So, kid, you're looking for a job, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what we do here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.10,0:14:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We write for time-honored and prestigious magazines.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.11,0:14:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Our next feature is on {\i1}Urban Legends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Go and interview people who have\Nexperienced something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, but I—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Any topic will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Like prophecies or getting spirited away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You kids like that kinda stuff, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.99,0:14:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.12,0:14:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an internet rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.37,0:15:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The one hundred percent sunshine girl.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunshine girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a sunshine girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's raining so much this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He ignored me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder there's such a demand for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.34,0:15:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.13,0:15:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, you've got zero initiative.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,She's got an interview. Go along and listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.43,0:15:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Me? Right now!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.47,0:15:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're on probation!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He's an intern.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No, really, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.90,0:15:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, sunshine girls do exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And rain girls exist, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.03,0:15:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,sunshine girls are possessed by the fox god,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.74,0:15:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and rain girls are possessed by the dragon god.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.99,0:15:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon god individuals drink a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,They yearn for water.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.42,0:15:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They're strong-willed and competitive,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but a bit careless and unreliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, maybe that's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.42,0:15:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Fox god individuals are hardworking,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.42,0:15:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,but too weak-hearted to be leaders.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Many are beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.43,0:15:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's definitely me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.43,0:15:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The weather is off-balance right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.18,0:15:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,so more sunshine and rain girls are born.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.89,0:16:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Gaia homeostasis hypothesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.44,0:16:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.44,0:16:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But, we must be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Messing with nature always has a cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.28,0:16:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever uses too much weather power, gets spirited away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.32,0:16:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.41,0:16:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.04,0:16:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A so-called psychic talked at length\Nabout fantasy novel like stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.96,0:16:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"If you use too much power, you'll get spirited away."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, that kinda stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.63,0:16:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, weather isn't some kind of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.67,0:16:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a natural phenomenon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.43,0:16:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, we're aware of that but \Nwe're providing entertainment here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.06,0:16:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all you've written so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.56,0:16:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.27,0:16:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Aah, but it's not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.11,0:16:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright kid, you're hired!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.73,0:16:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute! I never said I was—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a live-in job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.53,0:16:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Meals included.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:16:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it! Hire me, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What was your name again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Hodaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.58,0:17:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.25,0:17:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.00,0:17:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.50,0:17:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm underage, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's celebrate Hodaka's hiring.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.26,0:17:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.01,0:17:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the first meal I shared\Nwith someone since I came to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.81,0:17:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where my new life began.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a small editing company \Nrun only by Mr. Suga and Natsumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.27,0:18:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,My job was to manage all the office chores.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting from Mr. Suga's personal care.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.65,0:18:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Answering calls, filling receipts, transcribing interviews.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.90,0:18:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all you've written so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.90,0:18:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.91,0:18:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Suga is not at the office right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.70,0:18:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes we rode around town on Natsumi's bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.35,0:18:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They're looking for a sunshine girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? That's hilarious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,My sis's friend's a real sunshine girl.\NShe always calls her before a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.78,0:19:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, the weather balloon picked up something strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.07,0:19:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A swarm of moving objects among the cumulonimbi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.03,0:19:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all you've written so far!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.04,0:19:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't buy these unless they're on sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.79,0:19:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not at the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This paragraph's crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.71,0:19:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But this one ain't so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.79,0:19:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Suga, come on, wake up. Please wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My days were hectic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But for the first time, someone was relying on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, those rainy days in Tokyo, passed by in a flash!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.79,0:19:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,250)}Rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.33,0:19:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,180)}Rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.33,0:19:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,100)}Rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.34,0:19:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.96,0:20:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How's it going, Rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.84,0:20:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah? Good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.10,0:20:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an easy job.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.35,0:20:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, you'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.15,0:20:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.94,0:20:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get paid right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.61,0:20:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Our club's right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.03,0:20:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.33,0:20:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it a shot and earn yourself some bucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.21,0:20:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.17,0:20:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.47,0:20:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.35,0:20:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, wait just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.15,0:21:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.07,0:21:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Just keep running!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.20,0:21:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.99,0:21:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You damn brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey hey hey, you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.33,0:21:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,what do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.00,0:21:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You were forcing her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.17,0:21:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.21,0:21:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you retarded or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.42,0:21:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We had a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.60,0:21:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.52,0:21:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you the brat who was\Nsquatting in front of our club?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.35,0:21:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this, payback?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.36,0:21:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.15,0:21:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.03,0:21:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Get off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.66,0:21:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? A toy gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.20,0:21:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He's totally lost it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.77,0:22:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.50,0:22:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.84,0:22:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell was that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.30,0:22:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,To thank me for that burger?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.26,0:22:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's with the gun? Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.26,0:22:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.76,0:22:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I found it. I thought it was a toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.10,0:22:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like a lucky charm for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.69,0:23:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.02,0:23:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You pointed it at that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.61,0:23:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You could have killed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.27,0:23:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.53,0:23:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You make me sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.65,0:23:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.35,0:23:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I got fired, from my part-time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.11,0:23:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.69,0:23:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, nothing to do with that burger.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.90,0:23:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But still, I need a well-paid job.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.37,0:23:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I shouldn't have—
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.63,0:24:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.29,0:24:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.13,0:24:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a runaway, aren't you? I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.51,0:24:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But, you can't enjoy Tokyo if its raining all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.68,0:24:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.06,0:24:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here for a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.66,0:24:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, it will clear up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.91,0:24:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.39,0:24:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you mean—
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.24,0:25:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A sunshine girl!?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.74,0:25:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Hina. And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.12,0:25:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hodaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.91,0:25:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.24,0:25:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sixteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.41,0:25:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Younger than me?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.91,0:25:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.17,0:25:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,let's see,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.71,0:25:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,eighteen, next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.04,0:25:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.71,0:25:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You better treat me with respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.22,0:25:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, Hodaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.64,0:25:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.48,0:26:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, there's a fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.69,0:26:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.82,0:26:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.49,0:26:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm serious. It's this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.08,0:26:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.50,0:26:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.83,0:26:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.29,0:26:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a closer look.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.56,0:27:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.43,0:27:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that's too expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.68,0:27:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.56,0:27:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Check this, it's pretty incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.23,0:27:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.40,0:28:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They kinda look like fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.12,0:28:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They came down from the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.37,0:28:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But, they leave no trace...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.04,0:28:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, they disappear instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.59,0:28:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember what that guy we interviewed earlier said?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.46,0:28:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The sky is a deeper unknown world than the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.63,0:28:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A cumulonimbus can hold as much water as an entire lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.05,0:28:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it might as well harbor an uncharted ecosystem.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.77,0:28:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, these fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.89,0:28:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess. Fascinating, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.60,0:28:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That means,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.61,0:28:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,we can make some money off of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.44,0:28:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.40,0:28:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You are starting to sound exactly like Kei.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.74,0:28:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be boring when you grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.03,0:28:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't put off your sunshine girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.62,0:28:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going out on a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.87,0:28:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a date! I'm just—
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.50,0:28:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go look for a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.66,0:28:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Job? Don't you work here?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.62,0:28:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, I'm just hanging out.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.59,0:29:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,As I said, it's not a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.55,0:29:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand how you feel, Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.68,0:29:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But, she finally stopped talking about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.31,0:29:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be inconsiderate to meet her right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.44,0:29:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I have the right to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.32,0:29:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, you have a smoking addiction, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.15,0:29:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.86,0:29:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She's got asthma.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.16,0:29:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too inconsiderate.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.20,0:29:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I quit smoking a little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.54,0:29:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But still,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.16,0:29:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,you give off a bad impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.68,0:29:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It keeps raining all the time these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.93,0:29:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,She can't even play outside, and it's bad for her asthma.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.68,0:29:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for children nowadays.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.44,0:29:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We used to have beautiful springs and summers.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.20,0:30:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't live together, just the two of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.83,0:30:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.13,0:30:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.30,0:30:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't this be
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.05,0:30:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,the first time
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.47,0:30:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'm visiting a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.35,0:30:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Hodaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.85,0:30:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You got lost, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.23,0:30:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No, uhm... It's not much, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.56,0:30:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.90,0:30:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.48,0:30:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.44,0:30:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.99,0:30:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hodaka, have you had your lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.82,0:30:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet... But, you don't have to—
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.49,0:30:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.50,0:30:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How about I use these?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.00,0:30:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.33,0:31:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.51,0:31:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you live all by yourself, Hina?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.22,0:31:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,With my younger brother, actually. \NWe ran into some problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.02,0:31:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, problems?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.02,0:31:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about you, Hodaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.69,0:31:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.48,0:31:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I found it suffocating, that town and my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.99,0:31:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.42,0:31:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thought about going back?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.25,0:31:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.42,0:31:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.47,0:31:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for the delay!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.55,0:31:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Woha!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.80,0:31:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I forgot the chives!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.43,0:31:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,800)}Chives.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.64,0:32:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how's life in Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.89,0:32:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.56,0:32:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, I don't feel so suffocated anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.36,0:32:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Happy to hear that!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.65,0:32:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's dig in!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.58,0:32:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What? An earthquake?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.46,0:32:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.58,0:32:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.80,0:32:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hodaka, is this for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.92,0:32:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're a real sunshine girl, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.72,0:32:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.47,0:32:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You can clear up the sky just by praying, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.60,0:32:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.76,0:32:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you need a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.02,0:32:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I do, but I can't just charge people for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.23,0:32:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think the nightlife business is for you, Hina.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.90,0:32:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hodaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.57,0:32:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you looking at!?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.86,0:32:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not looking at anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.74,0:32:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't 5000 yen a bit too expensive?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.12,0:33:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about 3000 yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.45,0:33:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Considering living expenses, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.62,0:33:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we need some graphics.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.33,0:33:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'll draw them!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.17,0:33:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? A hippo?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.96,0:33:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a frog...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.51,0:33:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.18,0:33:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.80,0:33:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll post it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.89,0:33:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.26,0:33:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.06,0:33:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis, I'd like some sardines—
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.02,0:33:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Who're you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.94,0:33:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're that boy from the bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.15,0:33:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.77,0:33:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You two know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.36,0:33:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hodaka, this is my brother, Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.53,0:33:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi, this is Hodaka, my business partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.16,0:33:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, we've got a request!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.16,0:33:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You posted it already!?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.95,0:33:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They want good weather for the flea market.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.96,0:33:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.46,0:33:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute! Am I really going to do this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.09,0:33:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna rain tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.63,0:33:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the whole point!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.17,0:33:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.34,0:33:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Hina! I'll help out too!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.34,0:33:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How!?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.93,0:34:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina, please use this!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.15,0:34:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, don't need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.23,0:34:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Then, I've got another secret weapon for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.87,0:34:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, don't need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.75,0:34:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit messing around, Hodaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.58,0:34:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Who called those weirdos?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.30,0:34:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We thought they might bring good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.39,0:34:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't push yourselves too hard, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.68,0:34:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.98,0:34:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina, do you need water?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.44,0:34:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis, want some candy?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.77,0:34:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Just tell them to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.40,0:34:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.02,0:34:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, the sky's clearing up!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.11,0:34:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.62,0:35:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun's out!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.54,0:35:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been ages!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.25,0:35:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look! It's been so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.08,0:35:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.59,0:35:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.59,0:35:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.76,0:35:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.59,0:35:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a real sunshine girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.26,0:35:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I still can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.97,0:35:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That was great,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.26,0:35:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,even if it was a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.76,0:35:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't—
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.26,0:35:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Is 20,000 yen good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.27,0:35:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.10,0:35:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You get a bonus because you are cute, missy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.98,0:35:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much! We'll sell a lot more now.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.74,0:35:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.20,0:35:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That was amazing, sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.41,0:35:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel I can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.62,0:35:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool! Let's make money with the weather!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.79,0:35:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.22,0:36:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The human mind works in mysterious ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.64,0:36:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, you just need to see the sun\Nshining in the morning to feel energized.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.89,0:36:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A blue sky makes you feel glad to be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.65,0:36:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes you feel more in love\Nwith that someone by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.61,0:37:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a once-in-a-lifetime chance, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.53,0:37:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna wear a white dress under the blue sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.15,0:37:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,To watch the meteor shower!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.86,0:37:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It never wins on rainy days.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.45,0:37:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I worked so, so, so hard \Nat the sweatshop just for this day!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.29,0:37:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna play outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.04,0:37:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone had their own reasons\Nto wish for sunshine in a rainy Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.96,0:37:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina was only able to clear a small spot for a brief time.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.46,0:37:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But the sky would always answer her prayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.26,0:37:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She really is the one hundred percent sunshine girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.24,0:37:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It felt as if the whole town was dressing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.99,0:37:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And I thought, what a wonderful world I was born into.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.25,0:37:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon! Say cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.91,0:37:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Keep goin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.92,0:37:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, there's more!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.13,0:37:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.17,0:38:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.17,0:38:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.17,0:38:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.18,0:38:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.18,0:38:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.09,0:38:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.26,0:38:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We could really influence people with the weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.18,0:38:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized how much the human heart\Nis connected with the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.03,0:38:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.16,0:38:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,To where?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.79,0:38:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it canceled due to the rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.25,0:38:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already past noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.58,0:38:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,When will it start?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.79,0:38:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I even changed into these clothes for this.\NIt's canceled for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.04,0:38:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we go home?\NI'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.97,0:38:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I read online about the amazing\N{\i1}one hundred percent sunshine girl.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.18,0:38:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But are you sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.97,0:38:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Relying on a sunshine girl for such a huge event?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.89,0:38:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna rain all week.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.85,0:39:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't be able to postpone it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.35,0:39:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,In this situation, we're even willing to rely on a charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.91,0:40:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.99,0:40:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,With this job, as the sunshine girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.25,0:40:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I finally found my role in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.83,0:40:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.17,0:40:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe not. Or maybe not not.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.67,0:40:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe not, not not...?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.55,0:40:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.47,0:40:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.39,0:41:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, thank you, Hodaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.52,0:41:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Weather is a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.19,0:41:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The way the sky looks can move you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.53,0:41:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina really moves my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.24,0:41:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're my first choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.91,0:41:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're my{\alpha&HFF&} first choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.49,0:42:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're my first choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.22,0:42:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that project? Right, we've put it on hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.51,0:42:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, we're not going ahead with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.93,0:42:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Yeah, I'll do my best.\NIt was nice working with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.53,0:42:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.05,0:42:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Mamiya speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.05,0:43:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mamiya, It's Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.34,0:43:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to rush you. Regarding our meeting—
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.06,0:43:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late, Kei! It's an important interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.27,0:43:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,In a bad mewd, are we? No luck with work?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.15,0:43:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Hodaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.11,0:43:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Busy with his other job?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.69,0:43:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been neglecting work lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.32,0:43:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really. Just let him be.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.99,0:43:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not that busy anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.53,0:43:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He took in that cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.62,0:43:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You did the same with him, Kei.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.83,0:43:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.87,0:43:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You helped him because he reminded you of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.71,0:43:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how much are you paying him?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.80,0:43:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Just 30,000 yen? That's so low.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.59,0:43:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. It's 3000.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.59,0:43:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.93,0:43:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you for real? 3000 yen a month? That's exploitation!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.22,0:43:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Eyes on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.85,0:43:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna get sued! Actually, I'll report you myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.85,0:43:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, he gets food and accommodation,\Nand the company pays his phone bills. It's only fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.86,0:43:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.78,0:44:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no surprise he's got an extra job.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.66,0:44:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised it actually cleared up.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.37,0:44:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You kids sure are something.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.62,0:44:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a shame you're quitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.96,0:44:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She was caught on camera and we got flooded with requests.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.88,0:44:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We really can't do this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.96,0:44:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll stop for a while after this one last request.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.55,0:44:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks tired, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.35,0:44:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got guests, Granny?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.27,0:44:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.77,0:44:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thought I could help.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.77,0:44:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well aren't you young. So you're friends with Granny?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.48,0:44:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.40,0:44:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I requested for good weather on \Nmy husband's first anniversary.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.90,0:44:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it actually stopped raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.12,0:44:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be hard for him to return if it was raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.79,0:44:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Return?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.79,0:45:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They say the dead come back\Nfrom the sky around mid-August.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.51,0:45:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So that means, he passed away last year?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.64,0:45:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.64,0:45:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Around the same time as my mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.31,0:45:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You lost your mother last year?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.10,0:45:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.90,0:45:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, you should light a welcoming fire for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.36,0:45:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she will protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.44,0:45:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.74,0:45:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Riding the smoke, he'll come back from the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.54,0:45:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,From where?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.87,0:45:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,From heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.25,0:45:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1600)}There's always been another world up in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.63,0:45:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, this is what the Weather Maiden saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.97,0:45:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a mysterious painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.18,0:45:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Flying fish in the sky. And a dragon, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.85,0:45:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.23,0:45:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.27,0:46:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And this {\i1}Weather Maiden{\i0} was like a shaman, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.61,0:46:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.57,0:46:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Was she like a shaman?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.82,0:46:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.74,0:46:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Fixing the weather is the Maiden's job.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.49,0:46:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Fixing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.62,0:46:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds fishy to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.75,0:46:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this year's abnormal weather?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.17,0:46:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What do you mean {\i1}abnormal{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.75,0:46:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They all keep saying the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.01,0:46:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,"First time in recorded history."
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.89,0:46:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But since when did records begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.64,0:46:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe a hundred years at best.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.35,0:46:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How old do you think this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.27,0:46:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Eight hundred years old!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.19,0:46:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eight hundred!?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.02,0:46:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get too excited, Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.24,0:46:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Weather changes on a whim in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.86,0:46:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless of human needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.95,0:46:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't even tell what's the norm and what isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.99,0:47:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We're only allowed to stay temporarily\Nin the space between the sky and the earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.17,0:47:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,clinging hard not to be shaken off.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.84,0:47:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We used to be aware of this in the past, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.64,0:47:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,However, there's a thin thread linking us humans to the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.56,0:47:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the Weather Maiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.40,0:47:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A special girl who can take in people's\Nwishes and deliver them to the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.82,0:47:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,In ancient times, there used to be\None in every village and every country.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.58,0:47:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Kei, doesn't that sound like the sunshine girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.95,0:47:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you guys,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.83,0:47:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,do you even want to listen to my Grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.37,0:47:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It all sounds pretty far-fetched.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.12,0:47:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.17,0:47:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't seem far-fetched at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.67,0:47:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for such an interesting story.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.75,0:47:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But, everything comes at a price.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.18,0:47:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, a tragic fate awaits the Weather Maiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.39,0:48:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,One,{\alpha&HFF&} two, three.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.10,0:48:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two,{\alpha&HFF&} three.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.98,0:48:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.40,0:48:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Your turn sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.23,0:48:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,One,{\alpha&HFF&} two, three.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.90,0:48:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two,{\alpha&HFF&} three.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.69,0:48:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.11,0:48:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for keeping Granny company.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.74,0:48:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We're actually here because of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.86,0:48:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Play with us, Granny.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.62,0:48:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They seem to be having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.33,0:48:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How old are you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.04,0:48:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sixteen and she is...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.92,0:48:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She said it's her birthday next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.00,0:48:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? You've gotta get her a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.63,0:48:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Come have some watermelons, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.72,0:48:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.80,0:48:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.10,0:48:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.90,0:48:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.24,0:48:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit, but why?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.87,0:49:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.80,0:49:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea she was a minor, I swear—
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.18,0:49:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what this is about?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.69,0:49:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you it wasn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.15,0:49:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You made us run for no reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.44,0:49:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.99,0:49:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you tell us anything about this boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.74,0:49:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A high schooler?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.70,0:49:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he picked up the gun, that Shibata threw away.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.67,0:49:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, he might've written about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.01,0:49:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,On social media?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.55,0:49:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Kids write all sorts of stuff on social media these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.45,0:50:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.74,0:50:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Nagi! You're the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.95,0:50:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A ring would be perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.75,0:50:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Isn't that a bit too serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.96,0:50:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for sis' birthday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.25,0:50:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I did ask someone else for reference, but—
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.26,0:50:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What present I'd like?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.22,0:50:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hugs and kisses. Cash. \NA decent boyfriend. And a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.64,0:50:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She wasn't helpful at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.35,0:50:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye bye, Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.39,0:50:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later, Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.27,0:50:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hodaka, you're in love with sis, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.52,0:50:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? It's not like that—
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.98,0:50:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.03,0:50:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, being insecure \Nis the worst condition for a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.20,0:51:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,R-really?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.41,0:51:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Be clear before you start dating,\Nand be ambiguous later. It's the basics.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.04,0:51:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I call you {\i1}Master{\i0} Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.55,0:51:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis has been working hard ever since Mom passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.42,0:51:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she's been doing it for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.80,0:51:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,because I'm still a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.14,0:51:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I want her to do more teenage stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.31,0:51:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if you're the right guy, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.31,0:51:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.40,0:51:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, do you think she'll like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.66,0:51:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.03,0:51:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You spent three hours choosing it for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.58,0:51:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If it were me, I'd be very happy to receive it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.00,0:51:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish you the best of luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.67,0:51:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's sunshine girl job will be our last.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.22,0:52:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A man requested good weather \Nat the park for his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.72,0:52:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,After that,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.60,0:52:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give her the ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.03,0:52:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy, do it again! Once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.95,0:52:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, you'd better be ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.79,0:52:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.96,0:52:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't good for my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.96,0:52:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How did it turn out to be you, Mr. Suga?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.42,0:52:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know about my job?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.59,0:52:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew and you said nothing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.13,0:52:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And{\i0} you have a daughter!?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.30,0:52:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm quite surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.89,0:52:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's forecast said it's gonna rain for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.94,0:52:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,My daughter has asthma.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.65,0:52:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,She lives with her granny,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.23,0:53:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,who won't let me see her on rainy days.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.11,0:53:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing beats a gorgeous blue sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.20,0:53:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So Mr. Suga, you're Hodaka's boss, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.03,0:53:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, I also saved his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.49,0:53:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does she treat you like a little kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.66,0:53:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina is two years older than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.58,0:53:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Sixteen? Seventeen? Eighteen?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.54,0:53:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.50,0:53:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,—Isn't it?\N—No it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.63,0:53:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.76,0:53:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.01,0:53:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you gonna be in trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.22,0:53:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Does Natsumi know that you're married?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.01,0:53:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, what's up with you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.94,0:53:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hodaka thought you were my—
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.52,0:53:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}Mistress!?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.49,0:53:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you never told me \Nthat you were uncle and niece.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.78,0:53:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hodaka, that's a disgusting fantasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.07,0:53:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hodaka, you're a perv.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.45,0:53:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hodaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.04,0:53:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You looked at my boobs just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.46,0:53:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I did not!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.54,0:54:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Nat!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.55,0:54:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Moka! Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.46,0:54:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Daddy! I made a crown of flowers for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.63,0:54:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.05,0:54:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hodaka, you come here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.55,0:54:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, my master is calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.22,0:54:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hodaka's hilarious, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.77,0:54:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He's such a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.15,0:54:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think they're alike?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.32,0:54:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hodaka and Mr. Suga?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.23,0:54:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.15,0:54:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Kei ran away from home\Nand came to Tokyo when he was a teen.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.95,0:54:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He met his future wife and fell in love big time.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.82,0:54:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But she met with an accident a few years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.29,0:54:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He's still in love with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.71,0:54:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I've been dying meet you, Hina!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.84,0:54:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one hundred percent sunshine girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.59,0:54:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.89,0:54:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How I wish I had a skill like that on my resume!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.93,0:54:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate looking for a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.05,0:54:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I was in high school again.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.51,0:54:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanna be a grown-up quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.31,0:55:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, good to see you're doing fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.98,0:55:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I was actually a bit concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.20,0:55:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Moka, are you tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.37,0:55:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, take a breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.00,0:55:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.75,0:55:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine! Let's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.71,0:55:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.13,0:55:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we'll leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.88,0:55:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to spend more time with Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.26,0:55:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we all go and get some dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.43,0:55:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But—
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.39,0:55:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll go eat with Moka.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.93,0:55:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.97,0:55:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.56,0:55:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.48,0:55:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hodaka, take sis home.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.07,0:55:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina! Thanks for bringing sunshine today!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.99,0:55:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Likewise!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.07,0:55:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I could make you happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.59,0:56:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my god.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.42,0:56:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my god.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.30,0:56:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my god!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.90,0:56:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.40,0:56:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hodaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.90,0:56:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.99,0:56:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.32,0:56:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.24,0:56:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, nothing in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.70,0:56:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you gonna say?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.29,0:56:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hodaka, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.29,0:56:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.18,0:56:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.02,0:57:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha30}Hodaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.48,0:57:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.26,0:57:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I became a sunshine girl
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.60,0:57:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,on that day, last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.98,0:57:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I prayed for good weather all day long.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.24,0:57:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to have one last walk\Nwith my mom under the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.29,0:58:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It looked like a pool of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.04,0:58:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Praying with all my heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.67,0:58:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I crossed the shrine gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.19,0:58:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,When I came around, I was lying on the roof
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.23,0:58:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and the sky was clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.82,0:58:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Since then, I think I got connected with the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.59,0:58:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Connected
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.71,0:58:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,with the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.30,0:58:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hodaka, hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.76,0:59:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the late visit, it's the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.47,0:59:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The police?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.85,0:59:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you've never seen him?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.73,0:59:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been spotted around this area quite a few times.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.90,0:59:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know him. What has he done?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.49,0:59:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We just want to ask him some questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.03,0:59:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a runaway and his parents\Nfiled a missing person's report.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.12,0:59:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, Miss Amano, you're living\Nalone with your little brother, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.54,0:59:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.42,0:59:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a bit of a problem too.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.59,0:59:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Without a guardian, you—
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.67,0:59:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.55,0:59:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't cause trouble for anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.35,0:59:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.64,0:59:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll come back tomorrow with the social service.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.31,0:59:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do? They'll separate us!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.45,1:00:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hodaka! The police were—
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.62,1:00:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. Master, go home for now.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.13,1:00:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Suga?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.55,1:00:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Surprised by the new look?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.47,1:00:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my disguise.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.01,1:00:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The police came to my office earlier.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.97,1:00:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They're treating this like a kidnapping.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.52,1:00:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I denied any involvement but they still suspect me.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.10,1:00:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it, it's your severance pay.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.40,1:00:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come to the office anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.48,1:00:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll arrest me at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.32,1:00:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I filed for custody of my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.37,1:00:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a delicate time, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.66,1:00:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You should go back home tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.75,1:00:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Then everything will go back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.63,1:01:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be best for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.97,1:01:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to grow up, kid.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.60,1:01:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't stay here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.23,1:01:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But, where will you—
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.15,1:01:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, but—
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.90,1:01:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Anywhere will do as long as I'm with you, sis
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.07,1:01:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hodaka, you'd better go home before you get caught.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.58,1:01:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a place to go back to.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.83,1:01:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.42,1:01:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna be fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.25,1:01:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going back.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.51,1:01:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's run away together!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.36,1:02:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A sudden low pressure system is developing into a typhoon—
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.03,1:02:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's overflowing!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.78,1:02:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep calm and walk slowly towards the exit.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.01,1:02:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.47,1:02:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it a bit too cold?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.61,1:03:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.15,1:03:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get off.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.36,1:03:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ask Mom to pick us up.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.19,1:03:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's freezing!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.90,1:03:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.32,1:03:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's look for a place to spend the night.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.53,1:03:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, we're completely booked.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.87,1:03:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a reservation?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.62,1:03:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We're full.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.12,1:03:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the three of you?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.62,1:03:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have your IDs?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.13,1:03:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't accept unaccompanied minors.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.88,1:03:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not about the money.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.26,1:03:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't a place for kids.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.43,1:03:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.14,1:03:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you runaways?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.81,1:04:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis, Hodaka. Look!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.90,1:04:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Snowfall?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.50,1:05:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Hina really
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.96,1:05:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,connected with the sky?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.93,1:05:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm freezing!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.18,1:05:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Kei, how is it snowing in August?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.15,1:05:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, the world has finally gone crazy.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.02,1:05:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.78,1:05:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Kei, wake up. You'll catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.45,1:05:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka—
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.66,1:05:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka! And you too, Kei! Smile!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.76,1:05:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You look like an old man, Kei.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.34,1:05:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you grow up,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.05,1:06:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't switch between your priorities anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.06,1:06:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you saying? Where's Hodaka?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.52,1:06:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You kicked him out?!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.77,1:06:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding me, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.86,1:06:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, the police showed up.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.15,1:06:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotta protect myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.99,1:06:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you smoked a pack of cigarettes\Nand got drunk because you felt guilty?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.28,1:06:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so pawthetic.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.79,1:06:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,See, even Rain is saying it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.79,1:06:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so lame. So last century.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.62,1:06:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you stay away? You smell old.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.21,1:06:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You're just as lame.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.59,1:06:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina, was it?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.05,1:06:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If the story about the Weather Maiden is true,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.55,1:06:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,if she's really a sacrifice, then one day she will—
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.60,1:06:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's—
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.80,1:06:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, what should've I done?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.31,1:06:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to get so worked up.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.81,1:06:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a myth.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.48,1:06:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But, if it really was true...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.57,1:06:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If you could fix this crazy weather\Nwith just a single human sacrifice,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.66,1:06:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be fine with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.32,1:07:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, everyone would be fine with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.84,1:07:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.05,1:07:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous to walk around unsupervised.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.97,1:07:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all siblings?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.80,1:07:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.93,1:07:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going home.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.81,1:07:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a college student.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.31,1:07:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They're my younger brothers.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.18,1:07:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're their older sister.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.10,1:07:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you show me your Student ID?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.23,1:07:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have it on me.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.86,1:07:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's him.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.65,1:07:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And you? Are you in high school?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.24,1:07:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's quite a huge backpack.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.95,1:07:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you take your hood off?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.83,1:07:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.12,1:07:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Run away!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.25,1:07:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey wait!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.00,1:07:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop running away!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.05,1:07:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.38,1:07:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.26,1:08:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Resisting arrest!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.31,1:08:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.56,1:08:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit struggling!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.89,1:08:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hodaka!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.23,1:08:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, stop running!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.15,1:08:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina?!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.03,1:08:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}Please!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.04,1:08:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.17,1:08:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Hina!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.26,1:08:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Holy shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.05,1:08:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go take a look.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.01,1:08:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.10,1:08:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 28,000 yen a night.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.19,1:08:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,28,000 yen, can you pay it?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.40,1:09:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yeah, I'll pay.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.41,1:09:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like I'm a wanted man now.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.88,1:09:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's kinda cool!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.84,1:09:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really worried, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.63,1:09:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hodaka, you almost got arrested!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.39,1:09:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I totally panicked.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.34,1:09:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's hilarious.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.26,1:09:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing hilarious about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.18,1:09:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The room's spacious!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.43,1:09:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The bed's huge!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.43,1:09:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The bath's massive!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.19,1:09:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis, Hodaka!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.94,1:09:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a bath together!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.15,1:09:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it alone!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.24,1:09:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, Hodaka,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.40,1:09:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,let's take a boys-only bath together.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.74,1:09:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So{\i0} warm.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.95,1:09:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.21,1:09:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.33,1:09:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.25,1:09:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Switch!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.71,1:10:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of stuff here.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.71,1:10:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.05,1:10:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try them all, Master.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.72,1:10:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.76,1:10:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got my severance pay.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.97,1:10:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis, we're having an excellent dinner tonight!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.64,1:10:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.35,1:10:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the delay.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.65,1:10:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.37,1:10:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's dig in!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.24,1:10:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Lemme try some of that Hodaka.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.37,1:10:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The curry's yummy.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.75,1:10:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yakisoba's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.08,1:10:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I want some too, sis!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.42,1:10:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it too early, Hodaka?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.75,1:10:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Tastes better if you wait only two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.23,1:11:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If god really does exist, I have only one wish.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.44,1:11:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This is more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.32,1:11:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all we need.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.57,1:11:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll manage somehow.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.78,1:11:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So please, don't give us anything more.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.33,1:11:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't take anything more from us.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.58,1:11:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear God, it's my only wish.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.83,1:11:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Please just,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.29,1:11:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,let us be together like this forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.80,1:11:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.68,1:11:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy 18th birthday!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.43,1:11:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not too costly, but I picked\Nsomething that'd look good on you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.98,1:11:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.65,1:11:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.32,1:11:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hodaka, would you like for this rain to stop?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.78,1:11:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Um,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.57,1:11:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.67,1:12:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I was chosen to be a human sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.71,1:12:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.30,1:12:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsumi told me about the sunshine girl's fate.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.22,1:12:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She gets sacrificed and disappears,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.05,1:12:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and the weather goes back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.47,1:12:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.35,1:12:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They're always telling weird stories.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.85,1:12:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,People don't just disappear.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.49,1:12:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.74,1:12:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not looking—
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.75,1:12:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking at you, Hina.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.63,1:12:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.93,1:12:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The more I pray for sunshine,\Nthe more transparent my body becomes.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.93,1:13:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that if I die this way, \Nthe usual summer will come back.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.69,1:13:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of Nagi for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.94,1:13:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.15,1:13:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.03,1:13:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.15,1:13:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We will live together, the three of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.16,1:13:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hodaka...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.20,1:13:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina, let's make a promise
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.62,1:13:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,to always be together.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.71,1:13:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get a job.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.04,1:13:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll earn enough for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.54,1:13:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If you quit the sunshine girl job,\Nyour body will go back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.42,1:13:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So—
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.19,1:13:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.98,1:13:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I was still on the island.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.29,1:14:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.91,1:14:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I was rushing desperately, \Ntrying to catch up to that light.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.09,1:14:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Just when I thought I did,\NI found myself at a dead end instead.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.42,1:14:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time, I decided\NI wanted to reach that light.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.76,1:14:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And at the edge of it, I found you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.56,1:14:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.52,1:14:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The day I first met you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.44,1:14:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You looked like a lost kitten.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.37,1:14:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.45,1:14:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,you found a meaning for my existence.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.04,1:14:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I was happy to make people smile,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.46,1:14:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,so I kept working as the sunshine girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.88,1:14:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to have met you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.71,1:14:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't cry, Hodaka.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.57,1:15:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.28,1:15:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hodaka.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.70,1:16:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.12,1:16:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.00,1:16:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.87,1:16:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.08,1:16:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hodaka, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.88,1:16:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't find Hina anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.22,1:16:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, I just had a dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.93,1:16:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis was disappearing in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.81,1:16:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.85,1:16:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.86,1:16:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Open up!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.40,1:16:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What the—
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.57,1:16:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Morishima Hodaka, correct?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.40,1:16:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been reported missing,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.66,1:16:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and suspected of unlawful possession of a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.12,1:16:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to the police station.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.50,1:16:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Lemme go!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.41,1:16:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay—
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.41,1:16:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I said let me go!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.67,1:16:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hodaka!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.75,1:16:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.79,1:16:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit struggling.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.02,1:17:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep going.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.22,1:17:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the sky!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.22,1:17:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this for real?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.22,1:17:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sunny!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.18,1:17:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It cleared up!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.22,1:17:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The sky is so clear!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.22,1:17:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy I could cry!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.53,1:18:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.49,1:18:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.79,1:18:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,sacrificed herself?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.12,1:18:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina! It can't be real!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.33,1:18:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina..
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.96,1:18:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina!!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.34,1:18:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one more thing I would like to ask.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.09,1:18:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl with you who disappeared,\Nwas the fifteen year old Amano Hina, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.22,1:18:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Any idea where she might be?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.23,1:18:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina is fifteen year old? And not eighteen?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.52,1:18:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,She faked her resume for her job.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.36,1:18:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess she had to make a living.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.24,1:18:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But she's still in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.86,1:18:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's compulsory education age.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.91,1:18:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren't aware?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.54,1:18:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.79,1:18:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the oldest one.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.38,1:19:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pain.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.09,1:19:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,By any chance, do you know we could find her?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.38,1:19:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The sky has cleared because\Nshe sacrificed herself in exchange!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.89,1:19:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And nobody knows about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.85,1:19:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take this.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.31,1:19:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a pain.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.89,1:19:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we need a medical witness?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.28,1:19:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun is out.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.62,1:19:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy! Did you look outside?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.92,1:19:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.42,1:19:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a dream about Hina.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.17,1:19:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it was Hina who brought the sunshine back.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.05,1:19:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.06,1:19:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she did.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.35,1:20:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.19,1:20:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Detective, I've got a favor to ask of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.57,1:20:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.73,1:20:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go look for Hina! It's my turn to help her now.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.70,1:20:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come back as soon as I find her.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.70,1:20:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll listen to you in here, come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.33,1:20:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let Mr. Yasui know we're about to start interrogating.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.21,1:20:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.46,1:20:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.88,1:20:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.88,1:20:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone stop him!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.14,1:20:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.35,1:20:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That brat!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.18,1:20:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let him escape.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.68,1:20:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.15,1:20:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.99,1:20:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.11,1:20:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch where you're goin'!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.24,1:20:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheeky bastard.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.99,1:20:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Across the street!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.66,1:20:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yessir!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.34,1:21:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.35,1:21:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hodaka!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.35,1:21:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsumi?!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.56,1:21:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.35,1:21:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to find Hina.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.11,1:21:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hop on!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.36,1:21:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That little brat!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.99,1:21:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi called.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.87,1:21:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He said Hina has disappeared and you got arrested.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.71,1:21:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.71,1:21:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,At the Child Consultation Center.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.38,1:21:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kinda fun! We're outlaws now.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.26,1:21:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So, where to now?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.39,1:22:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Another visitor?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.40,1:22:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's girl again.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.02,1:22:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He must be quite popular.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.45,1:22:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.70,1:22:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayane! You're here too.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.03,1:22:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Kana, this is Ayane.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.66,1:22:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Please to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.70,1:22:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayane, this is Kana!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.04,1:22:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.79,1:22:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's Officer Sasaki.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.66,1:22:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be here with me all day.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.87,1:22:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.96,1:22:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're like a VIP, Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.59,1:22:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.30,1:22:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.05,1:22:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the sudden news.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.30,1:22:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,When I heard they took you in custody,\Nmy heart almost stopped!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.35,1:22:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Same for me! My heart's still pounding.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.64,1:22:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You can feel it, Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.31,1:22:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.11,1:22:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.82,1:22:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.44,1:22:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my first visit here and I'm kinda nervous.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.03,1:22:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.24,1:23:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I need to use the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.24,1:23:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.87,1:23:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, I owe you one.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.41,1:23:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, you even call your ex when you need something.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.30,1:23:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.92,1:23:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now look the other way, I need to change.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.23,1:23:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Keisuke Suga.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.19,1:23:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.65,1:23:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you guys again?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.31,1:23:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Summer's finally back the way it should be, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.65,1:23:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you I don't know anything about that runaway kid.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.78,1:23:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we check your office for a minute?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.07,1:23:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,H-hey, wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.62,1:23:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that for?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.45,1:23:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's flooded.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.33,1:23:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no one in there.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.71,1:23:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's a bit embarrassing, so—
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.21,1:23:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? He ran away?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.46,1:23:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,From the police station?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.05,1:23:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A run down building in Yoyogi?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.47,1:23:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's where she became a sunshine—
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.84,1:24:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Down!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.30,1:24:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina said she got connected\Nto the sky on the roof of that building.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.81,1:24:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if I go there, I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.15,1:24:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.53,1:24:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold tight!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.46,1:24:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.46,1:24:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsumi!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.25,1:24:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I awesome or what?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.30,1:24:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I was born for this.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.38,1:24:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.51,1:24:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I should become a speed cop!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.47,1:24:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}I doubt they'd hire you now!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.39,1:24:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,As for the reason for his escape,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.27,1:24:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he may be searching for the girl who was with him.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.23,1:25:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the story is quite strange.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.36,1:25:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The boy said she disappeared in \Nexchange for this good weather.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.49,1:25:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you actually believe—
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.91,1:25:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, I find it hard to believe.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.29,1:25:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But, he's throwing his life away,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.67,1:25:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,all because there's a girl he wants to meet so badly.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.18,1:25:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Makes me a bit envious.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.89,1:25:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point in telling me that.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.98,1:25:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Suga, you...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.36,1:25:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.69,1:25:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.28,1:25:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.11,1:25:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you are
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.95,1:25:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,crying.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.88,1:25:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.21,1:26:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We're jumping in!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.18,1:26:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't go any further.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.48,1:26:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, Hodaka!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.19,1:26:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Natsumi!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.28,1:26:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hodaka!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.41,1:26:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.14,1:26:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.73,1:26:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.77,1:26:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.57,1:27:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina, you're there, aren't you? Hina!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.15,1:27:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold up!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.20,1:27:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's on the tracks.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.36,1:27:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with him?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.62,1:27:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.37,1:27:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not safe!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.12,1:27:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.79,1:27:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.75,1:27:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.29,1:28:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.08,1:28:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.92,1:28:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.29,1:28:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone running.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.67,1:28:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll get arrested.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.21,1:28:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess he's an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.31,1:28:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.77,1:28:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Hina!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.11,1:28:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I made you do that sunshine girl job.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.44,1:28:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldered every responsibility all alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.82,1:28:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Hodaka.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.03,1:28:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like for this rain to stop?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.94,1:29:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Suga?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.90,1:29:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I was looking for you, Hodaka.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.57,1:29:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.24,1:29:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you realize what you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.62,1:29:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina has disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.45,1:29:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.99,1:29:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The sunshine girl job was my idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.75,1:29:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hodaka, you—
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.79,1:29:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my turn to help her now!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.92,1:29:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.30,1:29:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.21,1:29:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you—
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.96,1:29:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I can go to heaven through there!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.34,1:29:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.22,1:29:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.68,1:29:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,She's in the sky!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.97,1:29:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll use the emergency stairs—
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.72,1:29:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hodaka!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.93,1:29:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She can't be up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.48,1:29:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a grip!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.48,1:29:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Hodaka.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.90,1:29:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Just go back to the police station.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.90,1:29:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.32,1:29:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done nothing wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.36,1:29:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep running away, it'll be too late.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.03,1:29:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.33,1:29:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We've located the suspect's car.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.74,1:30:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Moving in to apprehend him.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.00,1:30:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'll come with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.79,1:30:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's explain everything to them, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.21,1:30:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go! Please!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.50,1:30:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Get off me!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.84,1:30:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hodaka, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.39,1:30:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.47,1:30:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hodaka. That's—
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.77,1:30:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Just let me go see Hina.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.83,1:30:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Morishima Hodaka!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.38,1:30:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Drop the gun!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.84,1:30:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey, wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.63,1:30:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a misunderstanding, I'll explain.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.30,1:31:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Hodaka?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.14,1:31:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.89,1:31:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Put the gun down, Morishima.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.39,1:31:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make me shoot.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.74,1:31:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hodaka.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.91,1:31:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon Hodaka, drop that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.70,1:31:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you guys?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.91,1:31:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just a kid!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.37,1:31:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.92,1:31:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why're you getting in my way!?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.92,1:31:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.59,1:31:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You pretend you don't!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.13,1:31:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I just
Dialogue: 0,1:31:36.80,1:31:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,want to see her
Dialogue: 0,1:31:38.93,1:31:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,one more time!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.52,1:31:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Got him!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.94,1:31:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.11,1:31:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Take your hands off Hodaka, you assholes!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.86,1:31:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard—
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.36,1:32:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! Hodaka!!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.91,1:32:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.79,1:32:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hodaka!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.62,1:32:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.04,1:32:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey—
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.21,1:32:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all your fault, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.63,1:32:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring my sis back!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.38,1:32:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh God.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.17,1:32:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.92,1:33:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0 ,2000)}Please!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.29,1:33:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Fish
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.62,1:33:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,in the sky?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.11,1:34:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}Hina!!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.88,1:34:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H50&}Hina!!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.71,1:34:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H20&}Hina!!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.10,1:34:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.82,1:34:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.44,1:34:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hodaka!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.62,1:34:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hodaka!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:52.91,1:34:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina! Jump!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.47,1:35:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina, I found you!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.47,1:35:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hodaka!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:10.85,1:35:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let go of my hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.14,1:35:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.70,1:35:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.91,1:35:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hodaka!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.17,1:35:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back together, Hina!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.34,1:35:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But, if I do, the weather will—
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.47,1:35:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.84,1:35:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done enough!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.26,1:35:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be the sunshine girl anymore!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:05.19,1:36:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if we never see sunshine again.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.11,1:36:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you more than any blue sky.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:12.74,1:36:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The weather
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.54,1:36:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,can stay crazy!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.95,1:36:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Make a wish for yourself,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.91,1:37:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.54,1:37:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.52,1:37:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hodaka.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:08.98,1:38:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It started raining again that day, and never stopped.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.82,1:38:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Slowly sinking Tokyo into the water.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:18.28,1:38:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's still raining even now,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.58,1:38:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,three years later.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.49,1:39:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I say?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:06.50,1:39:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Morishima!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.04,1:39:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, you're moving to Tokyo, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.55,1:39:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:16.05,1:39:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, ask him! It's now or never.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.85,1:39:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, Morishima!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:23.72,1:39:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I've always wanted to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.15,1:39:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Is it true that...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.65,1:39:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.65,1:39:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true that you're wanted by the police in Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:38.36,1:39:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:43.49,1:39:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That summer three years ago,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.51,1:39:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I was arrested and put on trial.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.00,1:39:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They put me on probation until graduation.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:55.38,1:40:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The island, my parent's house and the school\Nwere the same old places where I was supposed to live.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.18,1:40:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But each day, I was silently waiting for graduation.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:07.89,1:40:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Since that day,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:10.44,1:40:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen Hina.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.44,1:40:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea how I'll feel
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.45,1:40:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,after seeing how much Tokyo has changed,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.37,1:40:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,nor what I'll say to her.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.21,1:40:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I just need to find a part-time job.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.48,1:40:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.64,1:40:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of part time jobs...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.40,1:40:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still there!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:04.70,1:41:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a sunshine girl request from 2 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.46,1:41:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Look who's here. Are you alone?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.67,1:41:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the sunshine girl?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.76,1:41:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not a sunshine girl anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.17,1:41:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I came here just to tell you about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.35,1:41:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, please don't trouble yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:28.02,1:41:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You moved here.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.10,1:41:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You used to live in an older house downtown.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.64,1:41:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That entire area is underwater now.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.44,1:41:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.40,1:41:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you have to apologize for?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:39.94,1:41:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.45,1:41:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know, that whole area used to be under the sea.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.04,1:41:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Until about 200 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.13,1:41:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokyo was just a bay back when it was called Edo.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:58.84,1:42:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans and the weather changed it little by little.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.34,1:42:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So you know, I think it has just\Ngone back to how it was before.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.85,1:42:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:12.98,1:42:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been thinking that crap for three years?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:15.48,1:42:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that—
Dialogue: 0,1:42:16.86,1:42:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're about to be a university student
Dialogue: 0,1:42:19.02,1:42:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're still acting like a kid.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.94,1:42:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But that day, we—
Dialogue: 0,1:42:23.07,1:42:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You two caused all of this?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.20,1:42:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You altered {\i1}the nature of this world{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.16,1:42:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't gimme that crap, dummy.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.25,1:42:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Get off your high horse.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:36.58,1:42:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Check this, I went on a date with my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:39.75,1:42:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsumi and Nagi were in the way, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:42.63,1:42:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit sweating the small stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.59,1:42:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And why haven't you seen her yet?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.22,1:42:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you doing this whole time?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.05,1:42:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I was on probation and didn't want to trouble her.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.43,1:42:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't even have a cellphone.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.85,1:42:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm so nervous I don't even know what to say to her.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.65,1:43:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Rain?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.53,1:43:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You've sure grown up.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.28,1:43:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on now, get going!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.04,1:43:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got work to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.04,1:43:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Just go to her place already.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:14.87,1:43:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your time.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:16.54,1:43:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back again.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.04,1:43:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:20.54,1:43:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't sweat it, young man.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.96,1:43:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The world's always been crazy anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:42.57,1:43:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you positive.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:43.78,1:43:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.69,1:43:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking forward to the picnic.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.11,1:43:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:57.71,1:44:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It used to be under the sea.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:02.34,1:44:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The world has always been crazy.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:08.68,1:44:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So, nobody's to be blamed that the world is like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:13.18,1:44:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what I should tell her?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.30,1:44:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No! That's not right.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.93,1:44:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,On that day, I— no, we,\Nwe did change the world!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.18,1:44:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I made a choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:57.81,1:44:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I've chosen her.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:59.18,1:45:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I chose this world!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:00.19,1:45:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I've chosen to live here!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:02.15,1:45:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:09.03,1:45:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hodaka!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:17.45,1:45:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Hodaka?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:19.41,1:45:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:23.38,1:45:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.63,1:45:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hina, I'm sure
Dialogue: 0,1:45:28.13,1:45:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}we'll be alright!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:27.99,1:44:35.58,Ending_Alright,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}The whole world rests upon your tiny shoulders
Dialogue: 0,1:44:35.58,1:44:43.59,Ending_Alright,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(100,200)}I'm the only one who sees it and I'm on the verge of tears
Dialogue: 0,1:44:43.59,1:44:50.18,Ending_Alright,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}You notice that and ask "Are you alright?"
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.18,1:44:57.64,Ending_Alright,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}And I reply in haste, "I'm alright," but...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:57.64,1:45:01.98,Ending_Alright,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}Why is it that you're asking me such a thing
Dialogue: 0,1:45:01.98,1:45:08.11,Ending_Alright,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,500)}When it's you who's about to fall apart
Dialogue: 0,1:45:29.59,1:45:37.39,Ending_Alright,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(500,200)}The whole world rests upon your tiny shoulders
Dialogue: 0,1:45:37.39,1:45:45.44,Ending_Alright,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(100,200)}I'm the only one who sees it, and I'm on the verge of tears
Dialogue: 0,1:45:45.44,1:45:52.70,Ending_Alright,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}You notice that and ask "Are you alright?"
Dialogue: 0,1:45:52.70,1:45:59.49,Ending_Alright,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}And I reply in haste, "I'm alright," but...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:59.49,1:46:04.00,Ending_Alright,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}Why is it that you're asking me such a thing
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.00,1:46:10.09,Ending_Alright,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}When it's you who's about to fall apart
Dialogue: 0,1:46:23.06,1:46:30.03,Ending_Alright,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}Even though I'm small and incapable of obtaining
Dialogue: 0,1:46:30.03,1:46:37.24,Ending_Alright,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}this big dream I have now that's overflowing
Dialogue: 0,1:46:37.24,1:46:44.58,Ending_Alright,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}That dream is for you to be alright, I want you to be alright.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:44.58,1:46:49.04,Ending_Alright,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}I don't just want you to be alright
Dialogue: 0,1:46:49.04,1:46:59.51,Ending_Alright,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,400)}I want you to be the alright that's alright to you
