Dialogue: 1,1:47:41.35,1:47:47.94,Ending_Love,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}Born into this world with nothing in my hands
Dialogue: 1,1:47:48.27,1:47:54.40,Ending_Love,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}I keep on going around in circles in this gap of eternity
Dialogue: 1,1:47:54.73,1:48:01.20,Ending_Love,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}In the era where only the wise and resigned are the winners
Dialogue: 1,1:48:01.70,1:48:08.46,Ending_Love,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}Where can we find a moment to breath
Dialogue: 1,1:48:21.76,1:48:28.64,Ending_Love,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}Even the kings and gods turn a blind eye
Dialogue: 1,1:48:28.64,1:48:35.32,Ending_Love,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}But we all know deep in our heart
Dialogue: 1,1:48:35.32,1:48:42.07,Ending_Love,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}About the magic of courage, hope and bonds
Dialogue: 1,1:48:42.07,1:48:48.66,Ending_Love,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}Adults don't find use for them, so they look away
Dialogue: 1,1:48:48.66,1:48:56.05,Ending_Love,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}Even then, your will from that day is still here with me
Dialogue: 1,1:48:56.05,1:49:02.72,Ending_Love,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}As the central pillar of all my justice
Dialogue: 1,1:49:02.72,1:49:09.39,Ending_Love,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}Even if the world turns its back on us
Dialogue: 1,1:49:09.39,1:49:15.94,Ending_Love,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}You are here right now, standing your ground
Dialogue: 1,1:49:15.94,1:49:22.49,Ending_Love,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}I need to know if there's still anything that love can do
Dialogue: 1,1:49:22.49,1:49:30.75,Ending_Love,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,400)}I need to know if there's still anything that I can do
Dialogue: 1,1:49:35.42,1:49:41.59,Ending_Love,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}Because you had given me the courage
Dialogue: 1,1:49:42.09,1:49:48.14,Ending_Love,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}I want to use it all for you
Dialogue: 1,1:49:48.64,1:49:55.15,Ending_Love,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}Because you had shared with me this love
Dialogue: 1,1:49:55.44,1:50:01.40,Ending_Love,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}It would be meaningless without you here
Dialogue: 1,1:50:01.40,1:50:08.24,Ending_Love,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}I need to know if there's still anything that love can do
Dialogue: 1,1:50:08.24,1:50:15.54,Ending_Love,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}I need to know if there's still anything that I can do
Dialogue: 1,1:50:15.54,1:50:21.92,Ending_Love,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}Why were we shown dreams, even though we own nothing
Dialogue: 1,1:50:22.34,1:50:28.22,Ending_Love,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}Why were we given hope when our lives have an end
Dialogue: 1,1:50:28.89,1:50:35.10,Ending_Love,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}Why were we handed only things that would slip through our grasps
Dialogue: 1,1:50:35.85,1:50:41.82,Ending_Love,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}Even then, as we cling onto it, would you call us unsightly
Dialogue: 1,1:50:41.82,1:50:48.37,Ending_Love,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}Or are we beautiful, please tell us
Dialogue: 1,1:51:13.02,1:51:19.69,Ending_Love,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}All the love songs have been sung to death
Dialogue: 1,1:51:19.69,1:51:25.86,Ending_Love,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}In countless movies they've been told to death
Dialogue: 1,1:51:26.11,1:51:32.54,Ending_Love,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}Though you and I were born into such a barren land
Dialogue: 1,1:51:32.87,1:51:37.75,Ending_Love,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}But still, I need to know
Dialogue: 1,1:51:39.54,1:51:46.26,Ending_Love,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}There is still something that love can do
Dialogue: 1,1:51:46.38,1:51:53.77,Ending_Love,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,600)}There is still something that I can do
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.18,0:36:13.31,Insert_Celebration,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)\3c&H635D2B&\3a&H12&}I can't find the song I want to listen to
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.31,0:36:18.82,Insert_Celebration,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,400)\3c&H635D2B&\3a&H12&}At the start of this sullen day
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.61,0:36:26.49,Insert_Celebration,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}Just by hearing your exaggerated "good morning"
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.49,0:36:30.71,Insert_Celebration,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}Its strange how everything had changed
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.29,0:36:43.22,Insert_Celebration,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}I wonder why your words feel like the lines that you would see
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.10,0:36:56.19,Insert_Celebration,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,250)}Being recited at the climax of a movie and I like it
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.61,0:37:04.78,Insert_Celebration,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}If being coward is a sickness then I feel mine won't heal soon
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.78,0:37:11.29,Insert_Celebration,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}But you had appeared before me with the face of the savior
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.29,0:37:17.59,Insert_Celebration,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}It was you who had the key to my inner light
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.59,0:37:25.84,Insert_Celebration,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}It's not too bad to be living just to find out why that is
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.01,0:37:34.23,Insert_Celebration,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}It can only be you and there's no reason that it's not you
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.23,0:37:40.90,Insert_Celebration,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}So please don't go asking me "why is that so?"
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.90,0:37:47.28,Insert_Celebration,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(150,150)}Even though it feels endless, you finally offer a good answer
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.28,0:37:52.08,Insert_Celebration,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(150,200)\3c&H655310&}After I had 2019 other bad ones
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.12,0:37:59.54,Insert_Celebration,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,180)\3c&H655310&}Even though it feels endless, you finally offer a good answer
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.59,0:38:04.17,Insert_Celebration,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(180,200)\3c&H655310&}A good answer from the get-go
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.69,1:34:42.44,Insert_Grand,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}In exchange for wings that can fly in the sky
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.90,1:34:49.49,Insert_Grand,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}We chose to have hands which can hold each other
Dialogue: 0,1:34:50.53,1:34:56.17,Insert_Grand,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}Even then, we were fascinated with the sky
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.92,1:35:03.13,Insert_Grand,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}I wonder if its a sin to let dreams overlap
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.47,1:35:11.43,Insert_Grand,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}When summer looks at the fall that arrives
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.72,1:35:17.98,Insert_Grand,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}I imagine what kind of face it makes
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.27,1:35:24.19,Insert_Grand,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}Is it admiration, or is it love
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.69,1:35:30.74,Insert_Grand,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)\3c&H5F472B&}All while knowing that the dream won't come true
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.62,1:35:40.63,Insert_Grand,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)\3c&H5F472B&}Today is the one day in the millennia when gravity sleeps
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.34,1:35:47.22,Insert_Grand,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)\3c&H5F472B&}We stand in the blind spot of the sun, ready to depart from this planet
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.05,1:35:53.68,Insert_Grand,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)\3c&H5F472B&}When he had awoken from his sleep, we head to a place of no return
Dialogue: 0,1:35:54.27,1:36:00.06,Insert_Grand,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,250)}On the sound of "go" we slam our feet on the ground, to a planet far away
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.65,1:36:04.65,Insert_Grand,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,100)}Let's go
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.69,1:36:07.95,Insert_Grand,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(150,200)}Just a bit more, we'll reach past our destiny
Dialogue: 0,1:36:07.95,1:36:11.28,Insert_Grand,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}Just a bit more, we'll reach past civilization
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.41,1:36:11.70,Insert_Grand,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,500)}Let's go
Dialogue: 0,1:36:11.41,1:36:14.41,Insert_Grand,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}Just a bit more, we'll reach past our destiny
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.41,1:36:16.50,Insert_Grand,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}Just a bit more
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.41,1:36:20.62,Insert_Grand,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}We are the sails for our dreams
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.62,1:36:24.09,Insert_Grand,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}We get past the nights to approach the coming day
Dialogue: 0,1:36:24.09,1:36:27.09,Insert_Grand,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}Now, we are filled with expectations
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.09,1:36:31.01,Insert_Grand,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}Together we say "We'll do something about the rest"
Dialogue: 0,1:36:31.01,1:36:36.43,Insert_Grand,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}While we are not fearless, we won't stop
Dialogue: 0,1:36:36.43,1:36:43.02,Insert_Grand,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}Even if we try to avoid danger, we cannot help it when it arrives
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.02,1:36:48.86,Insert_Grand,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}But our love tells us, its voice tells us
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.24,1:36:52.20,Insert_Grand,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}It tells us to "go!"
