Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.80,1:37:55.26,Insert_Rain,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}In countless movies they've been told to death
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.93,1:38:02.64,Insert_Rain,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}Though you and I were born into such a barren land
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.64,1:38:09.07,Insert_Rain,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}But still, I need to know
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.95,0:17:48.08,Insert_Voice,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)\fad(200,200)}The afternoon when the wind had turned our helm right before our eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:56.63,Insert_Voice,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}I felt that I could do anything reckless, anything world-breaking
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.63,0:18:00.93,Insert_Voice,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}Be it my dominant or off-hand, I really felt I could
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.97,0:18:12.11,Insert_Voice,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}We'd go between "We'll manage somehow," "How much longer?" and "Are we alright?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.11,0:18:19.45,Insert_Voice,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}Like a pendulum, making sure to hang on tight
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.91,0:18:27.41,Insert_Voice,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}Let's see if we can use up that dream from the inside out
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.83,0:18:37.38,Insert_Voice,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}If we could change the world with love that won't be laughed at
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:41.64,Insert_Voice,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}Nothing's decided from the start, I don't need that
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.68,0:18:46.06,Insert_Voice,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}So please, God, quickly show me the next step
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.14,0:18:53.27,Insert_Voice,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}With an unbelievable amount of heart, with my terrible voice
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.32,0:18:57.44,Insert_Voice,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}I want to be able to shout and not rot away
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:19:02.03,Insert_Voice,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}Let me use up all the courage I have
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.03,0:19:09.29,Insert_Voice,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}If we could change the world with love that won't be laughed at
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:13.67,Insert_Voice,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}Nothing's decided from the start, I don't need that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.67,0:19:17.96,Insert_Voice,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}Let me use up all the righteousness I have
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.96,0:19:21.89,Insert_Voice,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}A greeting without goodbyes and future without helplessness
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.89,0:19:25.31,Insert_Voice,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}Is like a heart with lots of doors with no key in sight
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.81,0:19:29.81,Insert_Voice,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}I don't care how proud our future feels as it looks over us
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:33.31,Insert_Voice,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(200,100)}We still have something we need to do
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.31,0:19:38.86,Insert_Voice,,0,0,0,,{\be6\fad(100,250)}We want to use it all up, all the miracles we have
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.01,0:04:10.81,Italics,,0,0,0,,We're expecting heavy rain shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:26.57,Italics,,0,0,0,,For your own safety, please head back inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:41.44,Italics,,0,0,0,,Last year's instances of sudden torrential\Nrain were largely exceeded this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:03.96,Italics,,0,0,0,,Sudden downpours are expected—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:43.46,Italics,,0,0,0,,Everything the solicitors say is a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.46,0:08:46.04,Italics,,0,0,0,,Don't hand them any money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:47.67,Italics,,0,0,0,,You'll never get it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.92,0:12:23.22,Italics,,0,0,0,,He's a ladies' man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:13.24,Italics,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:15.83,Italics,,0,0,0,,I've never seen a mistress before.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.24,0:27:29.54,Italics,,0,0,0,,Kanto region is experiencing\Nrecord-breaking rainfall this summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.54,0:27:32.54,Italics,,0,0,0,,It's been raining continuously for two months now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.54,0:27:39.05,Italics,,0,0,0,,Forecast predicts heavy rainfall for another month.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.05,0:27:43.55,Italics,,0,0,0,,The Meteorological Agency said\Nit's an extremely exceptional—
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.49,0:32:53.11,Italics,,0,0,0,,Yikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.17,0:33:51.09,Italics,,0,0,0,,Widespread rain tomorrow—
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.74,0:39:57.37,Italics,,0,0,0,,The fireworks festival\Nwill start at 7 pm as scheduled.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.59,0:41:43.23,Italics,,0,0,0,,Yesterday's fireworks festival\Nwere blessed with a miraculous sunshine.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.23,0:41:47.23,Italics,,0,0,0,,But heavy rainfall is back again today like a backlash.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.23,0:41:51.61,Italics,,0,0,0,,The temperature in the capital is now 21ºC,\Nmuch lower than average.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.61,0:41:54.32,Italics,,0,0,0,,It's unusually chilly for August.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.32,0:41:56.24,Italics,,0,0,0,,Make sure you wear a jacket—
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.54,0:42:04.91,Italics,,0,0,0,,Be careful to not catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.91,0:42:09.42,Italics,,0,0,0,,Rainfall and low temperatures\Nare driving up the food prices.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.42,0:42:13.92,Italics,,0,0,0,,Lettuce is three times more expensive than last year
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.30,0:56:15.97,Italics,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't this be
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.97,0:56:18.90,Italics,,0,0,0,,the first time
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.90,0:56:20.31,Italics,,0,0,0,,I propose to someone?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.58,1:00:17.13,Italics,,0,0,0,,Temperatures have fallen sharply after the sunset—
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.06,1:01:54.85,Italics,,0,0,0,,A heavy rainfall warning has\Njust been issued in the Tokyo area.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.85,1:01:58.27,Italics,,0,0,0,,It could be the heaviest rainfall in decades.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.27,1:02:01.03,Italics,,0,0,0,,Watch out for floods in lowland areas.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.11,1:02:06.07,Italics,,0,0,0,,Rivers are flooding.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.07,1:02:08.03,Italics,,0,0,0,,The danger is rising.
