Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.55,1:02:31.56,Italics,,0,0,0,,You may get stranded.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.06,1:02:36.39,Italics,,0,0,0,,It's unusually cold for August.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.39,1:02:39.06,Italics,,0,0,0,,The temperature in Tokyo has fallen below 10°C.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.06,1:02:41.82,Italics,,0,0,0,,Cumulonimbi keep gathering above Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.82,1:02:44.32,Italics,,0,0,0,,In just an hour, it feels like an entirely different season.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.32,1:02:49.28,Italics,,0,0,0,,I repeat, a heavy rainfall warning\Nhas been issued in the Tokyo area.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.28,1:02:51.78,Italics,,0,0,0,,The low-pressure system over the Kanto region—
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.78,1:02:55.08,Italics,,0,0,0,,because of a stream of cold air at Kanto, the weather—
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.08,1:02:59.25,Italics,,0,0,0,,Heavy rainfall in central Japan even after dawn—
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.25,1:03:03.38,Italics,,0,0,0,,These erratic conditions will continue for a few weeks.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.38,1:03:07.09,Italics,,0,0,0,,This abnormal weather is\Nunprecedented and extremely dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.72,1:03:21.61,Italics,,0,0,0,,Due to transportation delays,\NYamanote Line trains are suspended.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.98,1:05:33.78,Italics,,0,0,0,,It's unbelievable, but it's snowing here in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.87,1:07:08.50,Italics,,0,0,0,,A heavy rain and snowfall warning has been issued.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.50,1:07:11.25,Italics,,0,0,0,,Do not go outside unless it's strictly necessary.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.25,1:07:13.84,Italics,,0,0,0,,Please follow the evacuation instructions.
